column2: SELECT TOP # s.z, p.objID, p.absMagU, p.absMagG, p.absMagR, p.absMagI, p.absMagZ, gi.d4#, gs.oii_#_reqw, gs.oii_#_eqw, gs.oii_#_reqw, gs.oii_#_eqw, gs.h_delta_reqw, gs.h_delta_eqw, gs.h_gamma_reqw, gs.h_gamma_eqw, gs.h_beta_reqw, gs.h_beta_eqw, gs.oiii_#_eqw, gs.oiii_#_reqw, gs.oiii_#_eqw, gs.h_alpha_reqw, gs.h_alpha_eqw FROM SpecObjAll as s   JOIN Photoz as p ON s.specObjID= p.objID   JOIN galSpecIndx as gi ON s.specObjID=gi.specObjID  JOIN galSpecLine as gs ON s.specObjID=gs.specObjID
